        <num>13-1-6</num>
        <content>
          <p>Parol contracts shall include only contracts in words as remembered by witnesses.</p>
          <p>(Orig. Code 1863, § 2681; Code 1868, § 2677; Code 1873, § 2719; Code 1882, § 2719; Civil Code 1895, § 3636; Civil Code 1910, § 4221; Code 1933, § 20-106.)</p>
